verbose_text: Interestingly, Litinskiy et al13 have demonstrated that human dendritic cells can induce CD40L independent IgG class shift through expression of the B-cell stimulator proteins : B-cell activating factor of the tumor-necrosis-factor family (BAFF) and a proliferation inducing ligand (APRIL).
evidence: expression of the B-cell stimulator proteins: B-cell activating factor of the tumor-necrosis-factor family (BAFF) and a proliferation-inducing ligand
